  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the cast-iron skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Season the cod fillets with salt, pepper, garlic powder, and paprika.",
    "Add the olive oil to the preheated skillet and swirl it around.",
    "Place the cod fillets in the skillet, skin side up if they have skin.",
    "Sear the cod for 3-4 minutes on the first side.",
    "Flip the cod over and sear for an additional 3-4 minutes.",
    "Remove the cod from the skillet and place it on a plate.",
    "Squeeze the lemon juice over the cod and sprinkle with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
